info.author: Parker Erickson
info.name: pyTigerGraph
info.summary: Library to connect to TigerGraph databases

vulnerabilities.details: The User-Defined Functions (UDF) feature in TigerGraph 3.6.0 allows installation of a query (in the GSQL query language) without proper validation. Consequently, an attacker can execute arbitrary C++ code. NOTE: the vendor's position is "GSQL was behaving as expected."

vulnerabilities.details: The User-Defined Functions (UDF) feature in TigerGraph 3.6.0 allows installation of a query (in the GSQL query language) without proper validation. Consequently, an attacker can execute arbitrary C++ code. NOTE: the vendor's position is "GSQL was behaving as expected."
